      I build accessible, pixel-perfect digital experiences for the web.
      Specializing in modern JavaScript frameworks and creating seamless user
      interfaces.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center">
      {
        socials.map((social) => {
          return (
            <a
              href={social.url}
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-border hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors"
